OL,3,C'Costly mistake' that some
OL,4,Cholidaymakers are making when
OL,5,Ctravelling abroad
OL,7,FGoing without cash when abroad could
OL,8,Fbe an expensive mistake for some
OL,9,Fholidaymakers, according to research,
OL,10,Fwith more than one in three having
OL,11,Ffound themselves caught out when
OL,12,Fneeding physical money.
OL,14,FSome 39% of holidaymakers have found
OL,15,Fthemselves in unexpected situations
OL,16,Fwhere cash was required while they
OL,17,Fwere abroad, according to a survey
OL,18,Fcommissioned by website Be Clever With
OL,19,FYour Cash.
