OL,3,C'Costly mistake' that some
OL,4,Cholidaymakers are making when
OL,5,Ctravelling abroad
OL,7,FThe research found some people who had
OL,8,Fto make an emergency cash machine
OL,9,Fwithdrawal on their last trip overseas
OL,10,Fwere charged an ATM fee.
OL,12,FSome people also said they turned to
OL,13,Fairport exchange desks for last-minute
OL,14,Fcash, even though they may potentially
OL,15,Fbe getting a worse deal than if they
OL,16,Fhad shopped around for their travel
OL,17,Fmoney and planned ahead.
