OL,3,C'Costly mistake' that some
OL,4,Cholidaymakers are making when
OL,5,Ctravelling abroad
OL,7,F"It's not about carrying wads of cash,
OL,8,Fit's about being prepared for those
OL,9,Fmoments when a card simply won't cut
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FMs Murray suggested packing a "cash
OL,13,Fcushion" ` a small amount of local
OL,14,Fcurrency that could be useful for
OL,15,Ftipping, local travel, or if
OL,16,Fholidaymakers end up somewhere that
OL,17,Fdoes not accept cards.
