OL,5,Ctravelling abroad
OL,7,FShe also suggested that holidaymakers
OL,8,Fmake sure they understand their card's
OL,9,Fpolicy on fees and currency conversion
OL,10,Fbefore they travel.
OL,12,FPeople may also want to check how much
OL,13,Fthey would be covered for by their
OL,14,Ftravel insurer if their cash is lost
OL,15,For stolen while they are abroad.
OL,17,FResearch released by financial
OL,18,Finformation business Defaqto in May
OL,19,Findicated that 91% of annual and 86%
OL,20,Fof single trip policies included cash
OL,21,Fcover as standard.
